arCallbacks.szOnCallbackCompleteScript:
function Start(idActorNPC, sConversation, idActorPlayer)

	Hydra.EventSend("EnterCity", actorLorathGate)
	Hydra.Wait(1)
	Hydra.ActorPlaySimpleConversation(convStartRites, actorYoungGuard)
	Hydra.ActorSetConversationList(actorElderGuard, "Frac_Prologue_ElderGuard_Optional")

end

function Start(idActorNPC, sConversation, idActorPlayer)

	-- The Sin Choice player variable as well as the player teleport
	-- is now handled via a script on the tablet board actor itself.
	-- This allows players to continue to interact with the tablet board.
	
	Hydra.EventSend("SinBurned")

end

function Start(sEventName, idActor, nUserParam)
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(actorLorathGate, locLorathWalkTo, "NPC_Walk", true)
	Hydra.QActorFadeAndDelete(actorLorathGate, 1)
end

function Start(idActorDamager, idActorDamaged)

	local followerLorath = Hydra.QuestGetFollower("NPC_QST_Lorath_Follower_Prologue")

	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(followerLorath) and Hydra.ActorIsValid(idActorDamager) then
		-- Don't play line if another player kills fallen too far away
		if Hydra.ActorDistanceBetweenActors(idActorDamager, followerLorath) <= 20 then
			Hydra.ActorPlaySimpleConversation(convLorathFallen, followerLorath)
		end
	end
end

function Start(idActorPlayer, sLevelAreaName)

	for i, Spawner in ipairs(tFallenSpawners) do
		Hydra.ActorEnable(Spawner)
	end

end

function Start()
	Hydra.Wait(1)
	
	local followerLorath = Hydra.QuestGetFollower("NPC_QST_Lorath_Follower_Prologue")
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(followerLorath) then
		Hydra.ActorPlaySimpleConversation(convLorathFollowup, followerLorath)
	end
end

function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)
	local followerLorath = Hydra.QuestGetFollower("NPC_QST_Lorath_Follower_Prologue")
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(followerLorath) then
		Hydra.ActorEnableAI(followerLorath, false)
		Hydra.QuestFollowerTakeOwnership(followerLorath)
		Hydra.QActorSheath(followerLorath)
		Hydra.QActorPlaySimpleConversation(convRitesStop, actorYoungGuard)
		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(followerLorath, actorLorathGate, "NPC_Run", true)
		Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(followerLorath, actorLorathGate)
		Hydra.QActorWaitForConversationFinished(followerLorath, convRitesStop)
		Hydra.QActorDeleteNPCClone(followerLorath)
	end
end

function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)

	local followerLorath = Hydra.QuestGetFollower("NPC_QST_Lorath_Follower_Prologue")
	
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(followerLorath) then
		Hydra.ActorEnableAI(followerLorath, false)
		Hydra.QuestFollowerTakeOwnership(followerLorath)
		Hydra.ActorPlaySimpleConversation(convLorathStop, followerLorath)
		Hydra.QActorSheath(followerLorath)
		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(followerLorath, actorLorath, "NPC_Run", true)
		Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(followerLorath, actorLorath)
		Hydra.QActorDeleteNPCClone(followerLorath)
	end
end
